## What is the purpose of the change

https://github.com/apache/dubbo/issues/4458#issue-463641024

1. clear resouces when invoker(AbstructProxyInvoker) is not in use: 

```java
protected <T> Invoker<T> protocolBindingRefer(final Class<T> type, final URL url) throws RpcException {
        final Invoker<T> target = proxyFactory.getInvoker(doRefer(type, url), type, url);
        Invoker<T> invoker = new AbstractInvoker<T>(type, url) {
            @Override
            protected Result doInvoke(Invocation invocation) throws Throwable {
                // do invoke...
            }

            // invokers need clear unused invoker
            @Override
            public void destroy() {
                super.destroy();
                target.destroy();
                invokers.remove(this);
            }
        };
        invokers.add(invoker);
        return invoker;
    }
```

2. clear RestProtocol.cliens by using map(key is url, value is client)

